Class Tag

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.energyxxer.commodore.types.Type
      • com.energyxxer.commodore.tags.Tag
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Exportable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BlockTag, FluidTag, FunctionTag, GenericTag, ItemTag
    public abstract class Tag
extends Type
implements Exportable
    Defines a Minecraft tag that represents various elements of the same category, and can be used to check if an element is one of various types at once.
